# Credentials that land in the repo root during local registry/SA-key debugging.
# `pem` is a real PEM private key (docker login -u <client-id> --password-stdin < pem);
# secrets never get committed — the vault is git-committed too (rules/vault.md).
pem
*.pem
*.key
